Package cwtwo

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Code
    An interface that provides a code and allows to add the elements of the code
    CodeComparator
    An interface that compares two codes.
    CodeGenerator
    An interface that generates codes based on colorbank and a specified number of pegs.
    Displayer
    An interface that handles the displaying of the different feedback and outputs of the game.
    Game
    A class implementing this interface is implementing a computer game.
    Greeter
    An interface that facilitates the setting of the game and the greeting.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CodeConcrete
    An implementation of the code interface.
    ColorBank
    A class that facilitates the storage of available colors and provides colors.
    FeedbackGenerator
    An implementation of code comparator.
    GameSettingsAbstract
    An abstract class with the different settings of the game.
    GreeterImpl
    A print screen implementation of the Greeter interface.
    GuessGenerator
    An implementation of code generator that generates a code based on an input guess from the player of the game.
    Mastermind
    An extension of the MastermindAbstract.
    MastermindAbstract
    An abstract class implementing a Mastermind Game.
    MastermindDisplayer
    An implementation of the Displayer interface for a Mastermind game.
    MastermindDriver
    A class that holds the main method of this program and starts the game.
    MastermindModule
    A class that handles all the binding for the automatic dependency injections in the mastermind program.
    SecretCodeGenerator
    An implementation of code generator that generates a random code based on a list of available colors and peg size.
